    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于Little Lilicia</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以耕田种地、照顾动物，还可以垂钓采集，或是去矿山探险……<br>在体验牧场生活的同时，与个性丰富的角色们交流互动，<br>尽情享受这款正统派牧场生活模拟游戏吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307270/extras/724c39de7210fa0d017fb1c4ff315a47.poster.avif?t=1770692985\" width=480 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307270/extras/724c39de7210fa0d017fb1c4ff315a47.webm?t=1770692985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307270/extras/724c39de7210fa0d017fb1c4ff315a47.mp4?t=1770692985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事概要</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公菲洛（可改名）搬到了可可镇开始新生活，<br>却因为镇长女儿比斯蒂的误会，<br>被当作是为了重振牧场而移居到这里的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >菲洛原本打算做一名普通居民，<br>他正想澄清这个误会，但在比斯蒂灿烂的笑容面前，<br>却怎么也说不出口，只好就这样开始了牧场生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着与镇上居民的交流日益加深，<br>他逐渐感觉到，在这里的牧场生活其实也不错。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >作为牧场主的生活</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >耕耘田地、播种浇水，精心培育并收获作物，<br>饲养鸡、牛、羊，获取各类畜牧产品。<br>走出牧场，还可以去山里采集野菜，在河边钓鱼，以及在矿山采掘矿石。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与女主角的恋爱、与居民的交流</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过聊天或赠送礼物，可以加深与7位女主角的亲密度。<br>当亲密度提升后，还能与她们约会，甚至发展成恋人关系。<br>此外，算上女主角，可可镇共有20多位个性鲜明的角色登场，<br>通过各种事件，你可以逐渐了解居民们不为人知的一面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307270/extras/1fa5774711e3a6fa640a98fa99a0a0c0.poster.avif?t=1770692985\" width=480 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307270/extras/1fa5774711e3a6fa640a98fa99a0a0c0.webm?t=1770692985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307270/extras/1fa5774711e3a6fa640a98fa99a0a0c0.mp4?t=1770692985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可以恋爱的女主角们</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307270/extras/368f4244158113dd5dce5d9887951801.avif?t=1770692985\" width=780 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307270/extras/ff01366a344223925a43f11bc09b06db.avif?t=1770692985\" width=780 height=251 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307270/extras/54e563206fa03c2c6d7cc035931e1736.avif?t=1770692985\" width=780 height=251 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307270/extras/a9818f8f2e0b4dcab7d3e4a2252e86df.avif?t=1770692985\" width=780 height=251 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307270/extras/4099d09cdf48264f57b354cc3a4f2111.avif?t=1770692985\" width=780 height=251 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307270/extras/36e9116e162c322da19fb7f4c0a25abd.avif?t=1770692985\" width=780 height=251 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307270/extras/b67125c38d8026c917d9aaed7fbae9c1.avif?t=1770692985\" width=780 height=251 /></span></p>",
